  ID: MenAtArms2
  Name: Brother Silvio, infirmary attendant
  Icon: {fileID: -2105629146, guid: d556a7f542c7d03429c5a535ce31a084, type: 3}
  Description: "He thought piety prepared him for gore, until he dressed his first
    blackening wound. While cleaning another man\u2019s flesh, he cut his palm with
    a soiled blade \u2014 he knows infection doesn\u2019t care about scripture.\n\nTreatment: 
    Heat the iron until red. Apply to the cut in a single burn. Irrigate with wine;
    bind in linen. Pray that the stink doesn\u2019t spread up his arm."
